  "texts": [
    "ChatGPT-4 demonstrates a slightly better balance between precision and recall, leading to a higher accuracy and F1score.",
    "This indicates a strong overall performance with a balanced approach to minimizing both false positives and false negatives.",
    "On the other hand, Google Gemini excels in identifying spam emails with a higher recall score, suggesting it is less likely to miss spam emails but may classify more legitimate emails as spam (higher false positives).This comparative analysis reveals the inherent trade-offs in spam detection performance between the two models.",
    "ChatGPT-4's balanced precision and recall make it a robust choice for general spam detection tasks.",
    "In contrast, Google Gemini's higher recall rate positions it as a preferable option in scenarios where missing spam emails is a greater concern than misclassifying legitimate emails."
  ],
